<article class="contact-form-card" aria-labelledby="contact-form-title">
  <div class="contact-form-card__accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="contact-form-card__intro">
    <div class="contact-form-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="contact-form-gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--brand-sun)" />
            <stop offset="52%" stop-color="var(--brand-coral)" />
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--brand-pink)" />
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <rect x="3" y="7" width="26" height="18" rx="3" stroke="url(#contact-form-gradient)" stroke-width="1.8" />
        <path d="M3 10l13 9 13-9" stroke="url(#contact-form-gradient)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="contact-form-card__label">Persönlich beantwortet</span>
      <h2 id="contact-form-title">Erzähl mir von deinem Vorhaben.</h2>
      <p>Deine Nachricht landet direkt bei mir. In der Regel antworte ich innerhalb von zwei Arbeitstagen.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-form-card__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <form id="contact-form" class="contact-form" novalidate>
    <input type="text" name="website" class="contact-form__honeypot" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" />

    <div class="contact-form__row">
      <div class="contact-form__field">
        <label for="contact-name">Name <span aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" placeholder="Dein Name" required autocomplete="name" maxlength="120" aria-describedby="contact-name-error" />
        <p id="contact-name-error" class="contact-form__field-error" hidden>Bitte gib deinen Namen ein.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form__field">
        <label for="contact-email">E-Mail <span aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" placeholder="deine@email.ch" required autocomplete="email" maxlength="254" aria-describedby="contact-email-error" />
        <p id="contact-email-error" class="contact-form__field-error" hidden>Bitte gib eine gültige E-Mail-Adresse ein.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form__row">
      <div class="contact-form__field">
        <label for="contact-phone">Telefon <span class="contact-form__optional">Optional</span></label>
        <input type="tel" id="contact-phone" name="phone" placeholder="+41 79 000 00 00" autocomplete="tel" inputmode="tel" maxlength="32" aria-describedby="contact-phone-error" />
        <p id="contact-phone-error" class="contact-form__field-error" hidden>Bitte prüfe die Telefonnummer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form__field">
        <label for="contact-subject">Betreff <span class="contact-form__optional">Optional</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="contact-subject" name="subject" placeholder="Worum geht es?" maxlength="250" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form__field">
      <label for="contact-message">Nachricht <span aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
      <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" placeholder="Was möchtest du entwickeln oder verbessern?" required rows="6" maxlength="6000" aria-describedby="contact-message-error"></textarea>
      <p id="contact-message-error" class="contact-form__field-error" hidden>Bitte beschreibe dein Vorhaben kurz.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form__footer">
      <button type="submit" id="contact-submit" class="btn btn-primary contact-form__submit">
        <span class="contact-form__button-text">Nachricht senden</span>
        <span class="contact-form__button-loading" aria-hidden="true">Wird gesendet…</span>
      </button>
      <p>Mit dem Absenden werden deine Angaben ausschliesslich zur Bearbeitung deiner Anfrage verwendet.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="contact-feedback" class="contact-form__feedback" role="alert" aria-live="assertive" hidden></div>
  </form>

  <div id="contact-success" class="contact-form__success" role="status" aria-live="polite" hidden>
    <div class="contact-form__success-icon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="29" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" />
        <path d="M20 32l9 9 16-16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Vielen Dank für deine Nachricht.</h3>
    <p>Deine Anfrage ist angekommen. Ich melde mich persönlich innerhalb von zwei Arbeitstagen.</p>
    <button id="contact-reset" class="btn btn-ghost" type="button">Weitere Nachricht schreiben</button>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .contact-form-card {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018)), #0a0a0c;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  .contact-form-card__accent {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0 0 auto;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--brand-gradient-warm);
  }

  .contact-form-card__intro {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .contact-form-card__intro > div:last-child {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .contact-form-card__icon {
    display: grid;
    flex: 0 0 52px;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  .contact-form-card__icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
  }

  .contact-form-card__label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .contact-form-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .contact-form-card__intro p {
    max-width: 48ch;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-form-card__divider {
    height: 1px;
    margin: 26px 0 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-coral) 36%, transparent), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07), transparent);
  }

  .contact-form {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .contact-form[hidden],
  .contact-form-card__intro[hidden],
  .contact-form-card__divider[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .contact-form__row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .contact-form__field {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .contact-form label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 650;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .contact-form label > span:not(.contact-form__optional) {
    color: var(--brand-coral);
  }

  .contact-form__optional {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contact-form input,
  .contact-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 52px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    color: #fff;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    transition: border-color 180ms ease, background 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
  }

  .contact-form textarea {
    min-height: 154px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .contact-form input::placeholder,
  .contact-form textarea::placeholder {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .contact-form input:hover,
  .contact-form textarea:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-coral) 28%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
  }

  .contact-form input:focus,
  .contact-form textarea:focus {
    outline: 2px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-coral) 72%, transparent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-coral) 64%, transparent);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-coral) 9%, transparent);
  }

  .contact-form :is(input, textarea)[aria-invalid="true"] {
    border-color: rgba(255, 99, 139, 0.82);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 77, 128, 0.1);
  }

  .contact-form__field-error {
    margin: 7px 0 0;
    color: #ff9ab8;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .contact-form__footer {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .contact-form__footer p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-form__submit {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 52px;
  }

  .contact-form__button-text,
  .contact-form__button-loading {
    transition: opacity 180ms ease;
  }

  .contact-form__button-loading {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 50% auto auto 50%;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }

  .contact-form__submit[data-loading="true"] {
    cursor: wait;
  }

  .contact-form__submit[data-loading="true"] .contact-form__button-text {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .contact-form__submit[data-loading="true"] .contact-form__button-loading {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .contact-form__feedback {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 13px 15px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 77, 128, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: rgba(255, 77, 128, 0.06);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .contact-form__honeypot {
    position: absolute !important;
    width: 1px !important;
    height: 1px !important;
    overflow: hidden !important;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;
    clip-path: inset(50%) !important;
    white-space: nowrap !important;
  }

  .contact-form__success {
    display: grid;
    min-height: 390px;
    place-items: center;
    align-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-form__success[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .contact-form__success-icon {
    display: grid;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    place-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .contact-form__success-icon svg {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
  }

  .contact-form__success h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .contact-form__success p {
    max-width: 38ch;
    margin: 0 auto 26px;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 620px) {
    .contact-form-card {
      padding: 26px 20px;
    }

    .contact-form-card__intro {
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .contact-form-card__icon {
      flex-basis: 46px;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
    }

    .contact-form-card__icon svg {
      width: 25px;
      height: 25px;
    }

    .contact-form__row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .contact-form input,
    .contact-form textarea,
    .contact-form__button-text,
    .contact-form__button-loading {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
